You ain't even picking up your phone","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:23"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "We just finished up big sis' funeral here","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:24"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "I wanted to tell you about it but the wild cat said u went missin!?!?","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:24"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "Big sis' dad even came He didn't blame you at all","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:25"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "He even said he wants to properly thank you if he gets to see you","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:25"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "Said that if it wasn't for you, big sis would've never gotten back up on her feet and return to the stage","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:25"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "Didn't hear things too clearly though That was about it since I was balling like a little girl","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:26"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "Didn't hear things too clearly though. That was about it since I was balling like a little girl","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:26"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "I know you like to be alone when you're not in a good mood","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:27"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "but don't go missing for too long~","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:27"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "Got some stuff I wanna talk to you about too","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:27"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "Anyway, shoot me a message will ya we're all worried about you","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:30"},{"MessageType": 0,"Content": "[JOE is offline]","Avatar": "","Time": ""}]

[{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "うぃーす","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:23"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "おーいなんで電話でないんだよ？","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:23"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "さっき姉御の葬式が終わったよ","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:24"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "ほんとはお前にも連絡しようと思ったんだけどノラ猫ちゃんがお前が消えたとかいうじゃん！？！？","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:24"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "姉御の親父さんも来てたけどお前のことは責めてなかった","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:25"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "もしお前に会ったらお礼を言ってほしいって","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:25"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "お前がいなければ姉御は二度とステージには立ってなかっただろうってさ","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:25"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "たぶん
いやあんまよく覚えてないんだけど
俺号泣だったから","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:26"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "お前もあんまり自分を責めすぎんなよ","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:26"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "こういう時一人になりたがる奴だって分かってるけど","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:27"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "早く帰って来い","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:27"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "話がある","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:27"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "てか心配だからさ","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:30"},{"MessageType": 0,"Content": "[JOEはオフラインです]","Avatar": "","Time": ""}]

[{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "yo, 在嗎?","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:23"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "欸你到底是怎樣? 電話都不接的欸","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:23"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "我們這邊剛結束大姐頭的喪禮","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:24"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "本來想跟你說一下 但野貓小姐說你失蹤了!?!?","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:24"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "大姐頭他爸也來了 他完全沒有責怪你","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:25"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "還說如果見到你要好好跟你道謝","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:25"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "說如果不是你 大姐頭沒辦法重新站上舞台","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:25"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "我沒聽得很清楚啦 大概這些 我自己都哭慘了","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:26"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "你不要太自責了 沒有人會覺得是你的錯的","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:26"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "我知道你心情不好的時候想一個人","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:27"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "但是別消失太久啊","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:27"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "我也有些話想跟你說","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:27"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "總之回一下啦 我們很擔心你","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:30"},{"MessageType": 0,"Content": "[JOE 已顯示為離線]","Avatar": "","Time": ""}]

[{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "yo, 여보세요?","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:23"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "대체 어쩌자는 거야! 전화도 안 받고.","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:23"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "우리 여두목님 장례식, 이제 막 끝났어.","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:24"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "원래 너한테 알려주려고 했는데, 들고양이한테 들었는데 너 실종됐다고 하더라!?!?","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:24"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "여두목 아버님도 오셨어. 
널 탓하거나 그러지 않으셔.","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:25"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "오히려 널 만나서 제대로 고맙다는 인사를 하고 싶다고 하시더라.","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:25"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "만약 네가 아니었으면, 여두목은 다시 무대에 설 수 없었을 거라면서.","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:25"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "뭐라고 하셨는지 확실하게 기억은 안 나지만, 대강 그렇게 말씀하셨어. 나 완전 눈물범벅이 되어버렸다고.","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:26"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "너도 자책할 필요 없어.
네 탓이라고 하는 사람 아무도 없으니까.","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:26"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "나도 네가 혼자 있고 싶어 하는 거, 충분히 이해한다.","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:27"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "그래도 잠수 너무 오래 타지는 마.","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:27"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "너한테 할 말도 있으니까.","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:27"},{"MessageType": 2,"Content": "어쨌든, 답장이라도 좀 해주라. 우리 다들 걱정하고 있으니까.","Avatar": "joe_os_02","Time": "AM 01:30"},{"MessageType": 0,"Content": "[JOE 님이 로그아웃하셨습니다]","Avatar": "","Time": ""}]
